		<div class="twelve columns">
			<p>I found <a href="http://wiki.tripsit.me/wiki/Drug_combinations">this great chart</a> showing how (relatively) safe combinations of drugs can be. I knew I could use my web development know-how to improve it, so I made it into a <a href="https://dillonjohnbrown.github.io/drug-combos/">web app</a>.</p>
			<p>My web app is a pet project of mine and is constantly evolving. I do a rudimentary form of user testing on my friends whenever I make improvements.</p>
			<p>I also put it's source code on GitHub for anyone to use in any way they want. This is for harm reduction and education, not profit.</p>
